@baseUrl = http://localhost:5252
@contentType = application/json

## Authentication Endpoints

### Register a new user
# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
	"username": "testuser",
	"password": "Test@1234"
}

###

### Login and get JWT token
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
	"username": "testuser",
	"password": "Test@1234"
}

###

@token = {{login.response.body.$.token}}

## Task Management Endpoints (Protected by JWT)

### Get all tasks for authenticated user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

###

### Get a specific task
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

###

### Create a new task
# @name createTask
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
	"title": "Buy groceries",
	"description": "Milk, eggs, bread"
}

###

### Update a task
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
	"title": "Buy groceries (URGENT)",
	"description": "Milk, eggs, bread, cheese",
	"isCompleted": false
}

###

### Mark task as completed
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/1/complete?value=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Mark task as incomplete
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/1/complete?value=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Delete a task
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
